data.description: Welcome to this spacious 2,853 square foot residence nestled on an expansive 1.19-acre lot. This beautiful home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an office, and 3 bonus rooms. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a well-designed floor plan that seamlessly blends functionality and style with new laminate wood flooring plus stained concrete flooring. The living spaces are generously sized, offering ample room for both relaxation and entertaining. The kitchen boasts modern appliances and ample counter space. The house also features a stunning enclosed add-on wrap-around back patio, overlooking the sprawling backyard and beyond, this patio provides a serene setting to unwind and appreciate the natural beauty of the surroundings. The 4 bedrooms are thoughtfully designed, providing comfort and privacy for all family members. Situated on a sizable 1.19-acre lot, this property offers plenty of space for outdoor activities, gardening, or potential expansion. The possibilities are endless, and the lush greenery provides a picturesque backdrop to this wonderful abode. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this spacious residence your own, where comfort, functionality, and the allure of nature converge to create the perfect living environment. No rear neighbors! Come live in the highly desired Wells Ranch! Schedule a viewing today and envision the countless memories you'll create in this inviting home.
